      "localizedDescription": "The whole ipa-bot pipeline in your pocket. Search every source you've configured, sign and inject in a couple taps, and keep tabs on what's starred, signed, and about to expire — all without opening Telegram.\n\nWHAT IT DOES\n★ Search — every source and channel at once, sorted your way, modded-only filter, offline cache when the server's unreachable\n✒ Sign & Inject — one tap from a result, multi-select for Sign All, tweaks injected before signing\n🔔 Stay ahead — starred apps flag when an update drops, signed apps count down to their 7-day cert expiry with a reminder before it dies\n📦 Library — stars, watches, sources, notes, pins, aliases, TestFlight watches, all in one place\n🗣 Siri — \"check my queue\", \"sign an IPA\", \"sign my starred apps\"\n📲 Widgets & Live Activities — queue depth on your Home Screen, sign/inject/decrypt progress on your Lock Screen and Dynamic Island\n🤫 Offline-tolerant — star toggles queue up and sync themselves once you're back online\n\nSettings split cleanly: BOT (your ipa-bot server + signing cert) vs. APP (theme, tab order, restart, danger zone) — no more digging through one long list.",
